        <abstract>
            <p>Sorry to hear of AS’s poor health.</p>
            <p>Would like to attend Aberdeen meeting [BAAS, 1859] but is unfit for so great an exertion. Has been told he has "suppressed gout".</p>
            <p>Pleased that AS remembers their 1831 geological trip, which made CD appreciate the noble science of geology.</p>
        </abstract>
